State of North Carolina
v.
Antonio Freeman No. 405P16 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 8, 2016 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, Joseph L. Hyde, Assistant Attorney General, Valerie Mitchell Asbell, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Attorney at Law, Southern Pines, for Freeman, Antonio.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 31st of October 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Northampton County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 8th of December 2016."
